## Detail.logUrl property

The URL of the logs for the specific execution of this function call.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
logUrl?: string;
```

## Remarks

This is different from the general logUrl from [FaastModule.logUrl()](./faastjs.faastmodule.logurl.md)<!-- -->, which provides a link to the logs for all invocations of all functions within that module. Whereas this logUrl is only for this specific invocation.
